OOOSOBOBBPJJJJJLJYLLYWWLLLLFFFFFFFFFRDDDDDRRKKKKKKYYYYYYYFLMMMMMMMMMMTTTTTTXXXXXXXXXXXXLLLLLLJJJJJJJJJJJJXXXXXXXQQQQQKKKKKKKKBYYYYYYYYYYYYFF
KKKPPBBBBPJJJJJLLZLLLLLLLLLFFFFFFFFRRRRDRRARRRKKXXYYYKKYFFLMMLLLMMMMMMTTMMTCCXXXXXXXXXLLLLLLLJJJJJJDDXXXXXXXXXQQQQQQKKKKKKKKKBBYYYYYYYYYYYFF
